messages.content: Your goal is to report the percent of Microsoft year-to-date stock price change. To do that, go to the website finance.yahoo.com. At the top of the page, you will find a search bar.Enter the value 'MSFT', to get information about the Microsoft stock price.At the top of the resulting page you will see a default chart of Microsoft stock price.Click on 'YTD' at the top of that chart, and report the percent value that shows up just below it.
